Now, what at this point am I to say about the Acts material in "Tears", the Xtian Golden Fish sign, the AI voice (Holy Spirit?) speaking of Hagia Sophia? My memories of actually being a secret revolutionary Xtian? The eidos of the Black Iron Prison (Rome) with us, the secret underground Xtians, timelessly attacking it? The reason given by the AI voice as to why I was helped in 3-74? Esp. "You have been adopted"? + the vision of the messenger substituting his blank white piece of paper for by bill of particulars drawn up against me, thus exculpating me. + - "UBIK"! Then my surd is the irreducable presence of the Cosmic Christ transubstantiating reality. (Treating it as a field.) Then what I call "the morphological arrangement" is that of the macrometasomakosmos not in spatiotemporal terms, exploded right down to the trash layer in our spatiotemporal world. But does this still explain the meta-abstracting via anamnesis? Yes, because it is Acts + Christ that are re-collected; + by "Christ" read Cosmic Christ: the macrometasomakosmos. "Re-collection" equals literal perception of it (him) + it/he is not arranged in spatiotemporality. Hence Acts + USA 1974 are two aspects (or continua) of one essence; he is that essence as world.


